---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "July 8, 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Azkar Tracker Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Azkar Tracker iOS app. Azkar Tracker collects no data — everything stays on your device."
>
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container legal__container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</span>
      <h1>Azkar Tracker Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal__updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p>
        Azkar Tracker is built by Zesencia Technologies. This policy is simple because the
        app is simple: <strong>Azkar Tracker does not collect, transmit, or share any of
        your data. Everything stays on your device.</strong>
      </p>

      <h2>What We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Nothing. Azkar Tracker has no accounts, no analytics, no tracking, no advertising,
        and no third-party SDKs. The app works entirely offline and never sends any
        information off your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Stored on Your Device</h2>
      <p>
        Your zikr counts, streaks, goals, reminders, and settings are stored locally on your
        device only. This data is included in your personal device backups (such as iCloud
        or iTunes backups) under your control, and we have no access to it.
      </p>

      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>
        If you enable prayer-time reminders, the app may ask for permission to use your
        location. Your location is used only on your device to calculate prayer times with a
        built-in solar calculator — it is never transmitted anywhere, and no internet
        connection is used or required. This permission is optional; the app works fully
        without it.
      </p>

      <h2>Notifications</h2>
      <p>
        Reminders are scheduled locally on your device using the system notification
        service. No notification data leaves your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Deleting Your Data</h2>
      <p>
        Deleting the app deletes all of its data. There is nothing stored anywhere else.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Because the app collects no data from anyone, it collects no data from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        If a future version of the app ever changes how data is handled, we will update this
        page and the "Last updated" date above before that version is released.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
        {" "}<a href="mailto:hello@zesencia.com">hello@zesencia.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>Zesencia Technologies is operated by Sublime Trade LLC.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding-block: 96px 120px;
  }

  .legal__container {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .legal h1 {
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .legal__updated {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
